// SessionCleanupDialog
// Modal dialog for deciding what to do with a session on closure: archive,
// delete, keep, or archive-and-continue. Disables all actions while processing.

FUNCTION SessionCleanupDialog(onAction, isProcessing) -> JSX           EXPORT
  Manages selectedAction state.
  Action options: archive, delete, keep, archive-continue (each with icon and
  description).
  Confirm button calls handleConfirm; disabled when isProcessing or no action
  selected.
  Shows spinner on confirm button when isProcessing.

---

FUNCTION handleConfirm() -> void
  Calls onAction(selectedAction) if an action is selected.
